    "More than 80 of RAI guidelines have been made publicly available to ensure a future in which AI systems hold up against this standard (Jobin et al. 2019), and Gutierrez and Marchant (2021) identified more than 600 soft laws around RAI.",
    "Studies comparing existing guidelines found that they are converging towards the same set of principles, even more in recent times (Jobin et al. 2019; Fjeld et al. 2020)."
